Installation Instructions
*************************

Copyright (C) 2008, Lee Thompson

Basic Installation
==================

  1. ./configure --prefix=/opt/ruby --with-ruby=/opt/ruby

  2. Type `make' to build the package.

  3. Type `make install' to install the programs and any data files and
     documentation.  You can use the DESTDIR enviroment variable for a
     staged install when packaging this software like so

           make DESTDIR=/tmp/rubygems install

